#

Spicy Honey Garlic Shrimp

20 min
$15
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanAsian

Course:

MainDinner

Tags:

QuickEasySpicySeafood

Description

A sweet and spicy dish that's quick to make and bursting with flavor!

Ingredients

  • shrimp, peeled and deveined: 1 pound
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • garlic, minced: 3 cloves
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • green onions, chopped: for garnish
  • lemon wedges: for serving
